---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Matter.js Game | Daridius">
    <div class="space-y-8">
        <header
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-6"
        >
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <a
                    href="/aplicaciones"
                    class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/30 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        class="h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-1"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2.5"
                            d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Volver a aplicaciones
                </a>
                <h1
                    class="text-4xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter sm:text-6xl"
                >
                    Matter.js Game
                </h1>
            </div>
            <div
                class="badge badge-outline border-white/20 text-white/50 px-4 py-3 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px]"
            >
                En Desarrollo
            </div>
        </header>

        <div
            class="aspect-video w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative group backdrop-blur-sm"
        >
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-br from-purple-500/10 to-blue-500/10 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
            >
            </div>

            <div
                class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center p-8 max-w-md"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 animate-pulse"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        class="h-10 w-10 text-white/20"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z"
                        ></path>
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-2 tracking-tight">
                    Próximamente
                </h2>
                <p class="text-white/40 font-medium">
                    Aquí habrá un juego interactivo creado con <span
                        class="text-white/60">Matter.js</span
                    >. Estamos preparando las físicas...
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Decorative background elements -->
            <div
                class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-32 h-32 bg-purple-500/20 blur-[100px] rounded-full animate-pulse"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-500/20 blur-[100px] rounded-full animate-pulse"
                style="animation-delay: 1s"
            >
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="max-w-3xl space-y-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">
                Sobre este experimento
            </h3>
            <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                Este proyecto explorará la integración de motores de física en
                tiempo real dentro del navegador. El objetivo es crear un
                entorno donde los usuarios puedan interactuar con objetos que
                sigan leyes físicas realistas, utilizando Matter.js por su
                ligereza y versatilidad.
            </p>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>
